description: The results of a COMPLETED analysis report generated with  StartAnalysisReport. For more information, see  AnalysisTypeReportResult.

parameters.name: FirewallName
parameters.description: The descriptive name of the firewall. You can't change the name of a firewall after you create it. You must specify the ARN or the name, and you can specify both.

parameters.name: AnalysisReportId
parameters.description: The unique ID of the query that ran when you requested an analysis report.

parameters.name: FirewallArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the firewall. You must specify the ARN or the name, and you can specify both.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the analysis report you specify. Statuses include RUNNING, COMPLETED, or FAILED.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The date and time within the last 30 days from which to start retrieving analysis data, in UTC format (for example, YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The date and time, up to the current date, from which to stop retrieving analysis data, in UTC format (for example, YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ).

nested_items.name: ReportTime
nested_items.description: The date and time the analysis report was ran.

nested_items.name: AnalysisType
nested_items.description: The type of traffic that will be used to generate a report.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: When you request a list of objects with a MaxResults setting, if the number of objects that are still available for retrieval exceeds the maximum you requested, Network Firewall returns a NextToken value in the response. To retrieve the next batch of objects, use the token returned from the prior request in your next request.

nested_items.name: AnalysisReportResults
nested_items.description: Retrieves the results of a traffic analysis report.

nested_items.name: Protocol
nested_items.description: The type of traffic captured by the analysis report.

nested_items.name: FirstAccessed
nested_items.description: The date and time any domain was first accessed (within the last 30 day period).

nested_items.name: LastAccessed
nested_items.description: The date and time any domain was last accessed (within the last 30 day period).

nested_items.name: Count
nested_items.description: The number of attempts made to access a domain.

nested_items.name: UniqueSources
nested_items.description: The number of unique source IP addresses that connected to a domain.

nested_items.name: Count
nested_items.description: The number of unique source IP addresses that connected to a domain.
